title: OneKey® MLS Appoints Three Staff Members, Recognizes Team Leaders
description: OneKey® MLS is pleased to announce several staff appointments and industry achievements. Gary Connolly has been named Senior Vice President of Business Development, Jeff Marzo has been named Senior Product Manager, and Laverne Brown has been named Tier 2 Support Manager.
